tech_specs: Shell (Woven): 100% polyester. Leather trim: Genuine cow leather. Lining (Woven): 100% polyester. Filling: 90% duck down, 10% feathers (Pekin Duck, Anas Platyrhynchos Domesticus). Finland silver fox fur (Vulpes Vulpes Fulva). Water-resistant & water-repellent.
Dry clean by leather specialist using oil based solvent only. Do not perchloroethylene.
